{"type":"message","id":"a83fa762","parentId":"3c2a5a6c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:30:29.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"工具调用成功，消息已发送。我应该告诉用户这个消息已成功发送，并总结如何给微信好友发消息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 刚才那条示例消息已经发送成功了！\n\n**给微信好友发消息的基本方式：**\n\n```\nmessage(action='send', channel='openclaw-weixin', message='你的消息内容', to='好友的微信 ID')\n```\n\n关键点：\n- `channel`: 固定为 `openclaw-weixin`\n- `to`: 好友的 WeChat ID (格式如 `xxx@im.wechat`)\n- `message`: 你想发送的内容\n\n如果你需要定时发送消息或群发，我也可以帮你设置。有什么具体的需求吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":20949,"output":169,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21118,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776846627198,"responseId":"chatcmpl-32f4d248-65c3-90cf-a982-8a0c7d43ba7e"}}
